{"id":203237,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/12/美国之音-阿富汗将和中国签署石油协议/","date":"2011-12-28T23:10:15Z","modified":"2011-12-28T23:10:15Z","title":"美国之音 | 阿富汗将和中国签署石油协议","content":"<div>\n<div> 2011年 12月 26日</div>\n<h2>阿富汗将和中国签署石油协议</h2>\n<div>\n<p>记者: 美国之音 <span>| 华盛顿</span></p>\n<div>\n<ul>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"20\" src=\"http://media.voanews.com/designimages/icon-email.gif\" width=\"20\" /></a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"20\" src=\"http://media.voanews.com/designimages/icon-printer.gif\" width=\"20\" /></a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/20111226-Afghanistan-oil-136225883.html#comments\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"20\" src=\"http://media.voanews.com/designimages/icon-comments.gif\" width=\"20\" /></a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://www.google.com/buzz/post?message=%E9%98%BF%E5%AF%8C%E6%B1%97%E5%B0%86%E5%92%8C%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E7%AD%BE%E7%BD%B2%E7%9F%B3%E6%B2%B9%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE&#038;url=http://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/20111226-Afghanistan-oil-136225883.html\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://media.voanews.com/designimages/icon-googleBuzz.png\" /></a></li>\n<li>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\"></a></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<ul>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://twitthis.com/twit?url=http://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/20111226-Afghanistan-oil-136225883.html&#038;title=%E9%98%BF%E5%AF%8C%E6%B1%97%E5%B0%86%E5%92%8C%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E7%AD%BE%E7%BD%B2%E7%9F%B3%E6%B2%B9%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE\"></a></li>\n<li>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div>\n<p>阿富汗同意与中国一家国营石油公司签署石油勘探和开采协议。</p>\n<p>阿富汗总统卡尔扎伊办公室星期一宣布，中国石油天然气集团(中石油)将与阿富汗的瓦坦集团共同开发阿富汗北部的三个油田。</p>\n<p>这个区域估计拥有8千7百万桶的石油储量。</p>\n<p>从理论上说，阿富汗的自然资源可以为阿富汗带来数十亿美元的税收。但是，由于目前的不稳定局势、基础设施建设的贫乏以及普遍的腐败，开采这些资源面临巨大的障碍。</p>\n</div>\n<div>\n<h4>相关文章</h4>\n<div>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<h3><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/20111129-south-sudan-134666978.html\">中国敦促苏丹、南苏丹解决石油争端</a></h3>\n<p>中国呼吁苏丹和南苏丹解决已阻碍南苏丹石油出口的争端。北京的石油进口有将近5%来自南苏丹。</p>\n<div>\n</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<ul>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"20\" src=\"http://media.voanews.com/designimages/icon-email.gif\" width=\"20\" /></a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"20\" src=\"http://media.voanews.com/designimages/icon-printer.gif\" width=\"20\" /></a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/20111226-Afghanistan-oil-136225883.html#comments\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"20\" src=\"http://media.voanews.com/designimages/icon-comments.gif\" width=\"20\" /></a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://www.google.com/buzz/post?message=%E9%98%BF%E5%AF%8C%E6%B1%97%E5%B0%86%E5%92%8C%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E7%AD%BE%E7%BD%B2%E7%9F%B3%E6%B2%B9%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE&#038;url=http://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/20111226-Afghanistan-oil-136225883.html\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://media.voanews.com/designimages/icon-googleBuzz.png\" /></a></li>\n<li>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\"></a></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<ul>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://twitthis.com/twit?url=http://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/20111226-Afghanistan-oil-136225883.html&#038;title=%E9%98%BF%E5%AF%8C%E6%B1%97%E5%B0%86%E5%92%8C%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E7%AD%BE%E7%BD%B2%E7%9F%B3%E6%B2%B9%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE\"></a></li>\n<li>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div>\n<h3>提交评论</h3>\n<p><span><span>*</span> 必须填写</span></p>\n<div>\n名字 <span>(任意)</span> <br />国家 <span>(任意)</span> <br />发送人留言 <span>字数限制在50